26 to store output but its error in variable to use it (2>)  "command substitution"
khalid@khalid-Victus:~$ ls /err
ls: cannot access '/err': No such file or directory
khalid@khalid-Victus:~$ ls /err 2> error
khalid@khalid-Victus:~$ cat error
ls: cannot access '/err': No such file or directory
