27 - to search in file about text but give the count of this text repeated (grep -c)
khalid@khalid-Victus:~$ grep -c localhost /etc/hosts
2  -> give you two
khalid@khalid-Victus:~$ grep localhost /etc/hosts
127.0.0.1	localhost
::1     ip6-localhost ip6-loopback
