40 - to create hard link from file like  original file (ln original symlink) its same file and content and modified
but if you delete the original file will not delete he hard link file

khalid@khalid-Victus:~$ ls -il ori* *link
12165090 -rw-rw-r-- 2 khalid khalid 12 سبت 29 00:15 hardlink
12165090 -rw-rw-r-- 2 khalid khalid 12 سبت 29 00:15 original
____________________________________________________________________________________________________________________
41 - to create soft link from file like shortcut to call original file (ln -s original symlink)
khalid@khalid-Victus:~$ ls -il ori* *link
12165090 -rw-rw-r-- 2 khalid khalid 12 سبت 29 00:15 hardlink
12165090 -rw-rw-r-- 2 khalid khalid 12 سبت 29 00:15 original
12165098 lrwxrwxrwx 1 khalid khalid  8 سبت 29 00:20 symlink -> original

symlink like pointer and if you delete original file will delete symlink


